column46: dad says child will fall asleep in car
driving around, unsure if child is asleep
arrived at a restaurant, dad says child just woke up
dad tells child she can fall asleep in the car since she has hardly slept
child might be asleep, breathing is steady
just got back home, dad takes child out of car
a lot of movement, dad seems to be carrying child
child wakes up near end when a phone notification goes off
movement slows and child seems to be falling asleep again.
